Evil Bitch was Batman-esque in her planning & execution and on the other side, MC and female lead didn't even know a threat existed. The story is bland and simplistic but the characterization of Evil Bitch is very strong, as strong as the art is good. Her goal is clear (Ruin female lead and take her place as tennis ace), her motivation is easy to understand (Jealousy+vindictiveness) and  she is extremely ruthless. She is a great character that is  unfortunately wasted in this mindless T&A fluff
